title: Nasdaq regains ground after choppy week driven by big tech earnings - Moneycontrol.com
content: Nasdaq regains ground after choppy week driven by big tech earnings  Moneycontrol.com
description: The Dow Jones Industrial Average fell 21.42 points, or 0.06%, to 35,089.74, the S&P 500 gained 23.09 points, or 0.52%, to 4,500.53 and the Nasdaq Composite added 219.19 points, or 1.58%, to 14,098.01.
